
Next to the src/ directory,
mkdir <project-group>/<project>
cp ProtoProject/* <project-group>/<project>/
cd <project-group>/<project>/

Use network_definition.json to define your circuit structure
adjust genPats.inc to produce the stimulus patterns that you need
Use activity.inc to define the sequencing of the simulation

If the default cell or synapse synapse models don't do what you need,
copy them into <project-group>/<project>/, adjust the as needed,
and modify Makefile to pick up your local copies instead of the src/ copies.

